{"word":"Angel (1)","slug":"angel-(1)","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Angel (1)</b> A Celestial Spirit.<br/> - Called Angel of the Lord<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=20'>Mat 1:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=24'>Mat 1:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=2&verse=13'>Mat 2:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=2&verse=19'>Mat 2:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=28&verse=2'>Mat 28:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=11'>Luk 1:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=5&verse=19'>Act 5:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=30'>Act 7:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=35'>Act 7:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=8&verse=26'>Act 8:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=7'>Act 12:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=23'>Act 12:23</a> <br/> - Called Morning Stars<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=38&verse=7'>Job 38:7</a> <br/> - Called Hosts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=2&verse=1'>Gen 2:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=32&verse=2'>Gen 32:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=5&verse=14'>Jos 5:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=22'>1Ch 12:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=33&verse=6'>Psa 33:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=103&verse=21'>Psa 103:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=13'>Luk 2:13</a> <br/> - Called Principalities, Powers<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?bo